        "created_at": "2023-07-22T08:30:25.350Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I wanted to leave my account offline on my old device without internet access, and log into that same account on my new device with internet access. If It wouldn’t log me out after 6 months then this would work. As it stands, it’s either lose all of my chat history or use a different phone number.</p>",
